cream stand
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number: 1
Definition:a platform on which metal cream cans are placed for collection [usually at a farm gate.]
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain:Rural
Region:[none]
